OL,3,CMidwife says maternity care in
OL,4,CSomerset is at 'crisis' point
OL,6,FA midwife in Somerset says she fears
OL,7,Fmothers or babies could die as a
OL,8,Fresult of what she describes as a
OL,9,F'long-standing staffing crisis' on
OL,10,Fmaternity wards in the county.
OL,12,FHer comments come on a day that the
OL,13,FYeovil Maternity Unit has closed for
OL,14,Fat least six months, for failing to
OL,15,Fmeet staffing regulations.
OL,17,FProtests were held outside the unit on
OL,18,FMonday 19 May to try and stop the
OL,19,Ftemporary closure.
