OL,3,CMidwife says maternity care in
OL,4,CSomerset is at 'crisis' point
OL,6,FITV News has protected the
OL,7,Fwhistleblower's identity, as she says
OL,8,Fit is vital people understand the huge
OL,9,Fchallenges midwives are facing on the
OL,10,Ffrontline.
OL,12,F'A chronic shortage of midwives'
OL,14,FShe said: "I'm scared that something
OL,15,Fbad can happen to both mum and baby,
OL,16,Fworse would be a fatality, I fear
OL,17,Fsomeone will die because of this.
OL,19,F"We have been facing a crisis at the
OL,20,Fhospital long before this closure,
OL,21,Fthere's a chronic shortage of midwives.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
