OL,3,CMidwife says maternity care in
OL,4,CSomerset is at 'crisis' point
OL,6,F"If women come in, there is supposed
OL,7,Fto be one midwife per-woman to look
OL,8,Fafter them, there's just not enough to
OL,9,Fhave that 1-2-1 care."
OL,11,FThe midwife added: "There are women
OL,12,Fwho are put in a room, and left there
OL,13,Fwhile we dart out to another patient,
OL,14,Fand if there's an emergency during
OL,15,Fthat period they can be in trouble,
OL,16,Fit's really difficult.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
