OL,3,CMidwife says maternity care in
OL,4,CSomerset is at 'crisis' point
OL,6,F"It puts people in danger, we need
OL,7,Fmore midwives to be able to care for
OL,8,Fthese woman appropriately, to help
OL,9,Fthem through their most vulnerable
OL,10,Fmoment in life and we aren't able to
OL,11,Fdo that for them. We desperately need
OL,12,Fmore midwives."
OL,14,FA mother from Taunton, who lost her
OL,15,Fbaby, has also described the system as
OL,16,F'broken'.
