OL,3,CMidwife says maternity care in
OL,4,CSomerset is at 'crisis' point
OL,6,FMel Scott's baby son Finlay died 15
OL,7,Fyears ago. Talking to ITV News, she
OL,8,Fsaid: "I was admitted to the anti-
OL,9,Fnatal ward where there were only two
OL,10,Fmidwives on duty looking after a whole
OL,11,Fward of people.
OL,13,F"I was watching my babies heartbeat on
OL,14,Fthe monitor, it slowed down and then
OL,15,Fit stopped, the midwife got a doctor
OL,16,Fto come, but there was a delay because
OL,17,Fthere was only one doctor and he was
OL,18,Fin theatre at the time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
