OL,3,CMidwife says maternity care in
OL,4,CSomerset is at 'crisis' point
OL,6,F"It doesn't matter how good the
OL,7,Fmidwives are, if there's not enough of
OL,8,Fthem, if there's not enough equipment
OL,9,For resources, there really struggling
OL,10,Fin a broken system."
OL,12,FThese concerns come amid a growing
OL,13,Fnumber of issues in maternity care
OL,14,Facross the UK, with a report last year
OL,15,Ffinding almost half of inspected
OL,16,Fservices across NHS England were
OL,17,F'inadequate' or 'required improvement'.
