OL,3,CMidwife says maternity care in
OL,4,CSomerset is at 'crisis' point
OL,6,FFrom Monday 19 May, the only maternity
OL,7,Funit in Somerset remaining fully
OL,8,Foperational will be at Taunton's
OL,9,FMusgrove Park hospital, with
OL,10,Falternatives available in Bath and
OL,11,FDorchester.
OL,13,FThe Yeovil unit currently supports
OL,14,Fmore than 1,200 births annually.
OL,16,FOther maternity services, including
OL,17,Fantenatal appointments, are expected
OL,18,Fto continue at Yeovil during the six-
OL,19,Fmonth closure period.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
