OL,3,CMidwife says maternity care in
OL,4,CSomerset is at 'crisis' point
OL,6,FThe Somerset NHS Foundation Trust says
OL,7,Fthere are no shortage of midwives in
OL,8,FSomerset but acknowledged there is a
OL,9,Fshortage of paediatricians in Yeovil -
OL,10,Fwhich led to the temporary closure.
OL,12,FChief Executive for Somerset NHS
OL,13,FFoundation Trust, Peter Lewis, said:
OL,14,F"We have taken this really difficult
OL,15,Fdecision to close this baby care unit
OL,16,Fat Yeovil Hospital.
OL,18,F"That's cause we have concerns round
OL,19,Four paediatric service. What that also
OL,20,Fmeans it has a knock on effect on our
OL,21,Fbirthing unit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
