OL,3,CMidwife says maternity care in
OL,4,CSomerset is at 'crisis' point
OL,6,F"We are really sorry to local
OL,7,Fpopulations, to families, who
OL,8,Funderstandably are anxious and
OL,9,Fconcerned about what this means for
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"We want to provide the right service
OL,13,Fto the local population, cause we have
OL,14,Fsignificant plans to resolve these
OL,15,Fissues, we need 6 months, it's hard to
OL,16,Fgive absolute guarantee on when we
OL,17,Fwill reopen, but thats what we are
OL,18,Fworking towards.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
